note.original: ayaṃ saṅkhyā vicāretabbā, nalokiyanalokuttaradhammo nāma natthi
note.snippet: Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokuttaro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokiyo dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Lokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca nalokiyo ca nalokuttaro ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.)
